[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    163[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The opening paragraph is excellent: "There's a supply closet on every hospital floor. Inside it, someone has taped a handwritten note to the shelf..." This is exactly the right voice. The reader is immediately grounded in a real scenario. The progression from gut-feel to math is well-paced. The "Honest Take" section hits the right notes: "Garbage in, garbage out, but with a veneer of mathematical rigor that makes it harder to spot" is peak CC voice.
